{"code":200,"status":"OK","data":{"number":74,"name":"\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0645\u064f\u062f\u0651\u064e\u062b\u0651\u0650\u0631\u0650","englishName":"Al-Muddaththir","englishNameTranslation":"The Cloaked One","revelationType":"Meccan","numberOfAyahs":56,"ayahs":[{"number":5496,"text":"O, toi (Muhammad)! Le rev\u00eatu d'un manteau!","numberInSurah":1,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5497,"text":"L\u00e8ve-toi et avertis.","numberInSurah":2,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5498,"text":"Et de ton Seigneur, c\u00e9l\u00e8bre la grandeur.","numberInSurah":3,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5499,"text":"Et tes v\u00eatements, purifie-les.","numberInSurah":4,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5500,"text":"Et de tout p\u00e9ch\u00e9, \u00e9carte-toi.","numberInSurah":5,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5501,"text":"Et ne donne pas dans le but de recevoir davantage.","numberInSurah":6,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5502,"text":"Et pour ton Seigneur, endure.","numberInSurah":7,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5503,"text":"Quand on sonnera du Clairon,","numberInSurah":8,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5504,"text":"alors, ce jour-l\u00e0 sera un jour difficile,","numberInSurah":9,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5505,"text":"pas facile pour les m\u00e9cr\u00e9ants.","numberInSurah":10,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5506,"text":"Laisse-Moi avec celui que J'ai cr\u00e9\u00e9 seul,","numberInSurah":11,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5507,"text":"et \u00e0 qui J'ai donn\u00e9 des biens \u00e9tendus,","numberInSurah":12,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5508,"text":"et des enfants qui lui tiennent toujours compagnie,","numberInSurah":13,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5509,"text":"pour qui aussi J'ai aplani toutes difficult\u00e9s","numberInSurah":14,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5510,"text":"Cependant, il convoite [de Moi] que Je lui donne davantage.","numberInSurah":15,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5511,"text":"Pas du tout! Car il reniait nos versets (le Coran) avec ent\u00eatement.","numberInSurah":16,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5512,"text":"Je vais le contraindre \u00e0 gravir une pente.","numberInSurah":17,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":575,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5513,"text":"Il a r\u00e9fl\u00e9chi. Et il a d\u00e9cid\u00e9.","numberInSurah":18,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5514,"text":"Qu'il p\u00e9risse! Comme il a d\u00e9cid\u00e9!","numberInSurah":19,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5515,"text":"Encore une fois, qu'il p\u00e9risse; comme il a d\u00e9cid\u00e9!","numberInSurah":20,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5516,"text":"Ensuite, il a regard\u00e9.","numberInSurah":21,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5517,"text":"Et il s'est renfrogn\u00e9 et a durci son visage.","numberInSurah":22,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5518,"text":"Ensuite il a tourn\u00e9 le dos et s'est enfl\u00e9 d'orgueil","numberInSurah":23,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5519,"text":"Puis il a dit: \u00abCeci (le Coran) n'est que magie apprise","numberInSurah":24,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5520,"text":"ce n'est l\u00e0 que la parole d'un humain\u00bb.","numberInSurah":25,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5521,"text":"Je vais le br\u00fbler dans le Feu intense (Saqar).","numberInSurah":26,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5522,"text":"Et qui te dira ce qu'est Saqar?","numberInSurah":27,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5523,"text":"Il ne laisse rien et n'\u00e9pargne rien;","numberInSurah":28,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5524,"text":"Il br\u00fble la peau et la noircit.","numberInSurah":29,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5525,"text":"Ils sont dix neuf \u00e0 y veiller.","numberInSurah":30,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5526,"text":"Nous n'avons assign\u00e9 comme gardiens du Feu que des Anges. Cependant, Nous n'en avons fix\u00e9 le nombre que pour \u00e9prouver les m\u00e9cr\u00e9ants, et aussi afin que ceux \u00e0 qui le Livre a \u00e9t\u00e9 apport\u00e9 soient convaincus, et que croisse la foi de ceux qui croient, et que ceux \u00e0 qui le Livre a \u00e9t\u00e9 apport\u00e9 et les croyants n'aient point de doute; et pour que ceux qui ont au c\u0153ur quelque maladie ainsi que les m\u00e9cr\u00e9ants disent: \u00abQu'a donc voulu Allah par cette parabole?\u00bb C'est ainsi qu'Allah \u00e9gare qui Il veut et guide qui Il veut. Nul ne conna\u00eet les arm\u00e9es de ton Seigneur, \u00e0 part Lui. Et ce n'est l\u00e0 qu'un rappel pour les humains.","numberInSurah":31,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":510,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5527,"text":"Non!... Par la lune!","numberInSurah":32,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5528,"text":"Et par la nuit quand elle se retire!","numberInSurah":33,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5529,"text":"Et par l'aurore quand elle se d\u00e9couvre!","numberInSurah":34,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5530,"text":"[Saqar] est l'un des plus grands [malheurs]","numberInSurah":35,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5531,"text":"un avertissement, pour les humains.","numberInSurah":36,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5532,"text":"Pour qui d'entre vous, veut avancer ou reculer.","numberInSurah":37,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5533,"text":"Toute \u00e2me est l'otage de ce qu'elle a acquis.","numberInSurah":38,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5534,"text":"Sauf les gens de la droite (les \u00e9lus):","numberInSurah":39,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5535,"text":"dans des Jardins, ils s'interrogeront","numberInSurah":40,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5536,"text":"au sujet des criminels:","numberInSurah":41,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5537,"text":"\u00abQu'est-ce qui vous a achemin\u00e9s \u00e0 Saqar?\u00bb","numberInSurah":42,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5538,"text":"Ils diront: \u00abNous n'\u00e9tions pas de ceux qui faisaient la Sal\u00e2t,","numberInSurah":43,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5539,"text":"et nous ne nourrissions pas le pauvre,","numberInSurah":44,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5540,"text":"et nous nous associions \u00e0 ceux qui tenaient des conversations futiles,","numberInSurah":45,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5541,"text":"et nous traitions de mensonge le jour de la R\u00e9tribution,","numberInSurah":46,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5542,"text":"jusqu'\u00e0 ce que nous v\u00eent la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 \u00e9vidente [la mort]\u00bb.","numberInSurah":47,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":576,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5543,"text":"Ne leur profitera point donc, l'intercession des intercesseurs.","numberInSurah":48,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":577,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5544,"text":"Qu'ont-ils \u00e0 se d\u00e9tourner du Rappel?","numberInSurah":49,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":577,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5545,"text":"Ils sont comme des onagres \u00e9pouvant\u00e9s,","numberInSurah":50,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":577,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5546,"text":"s'enfuyant devant un lion.","numberInSurah":51,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":577,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5547,"text":"Chacun d'eux voudrait plut\u00f4t qu'on lui apporte des feuilles tout \u00e9tal\u00e9es.","numberInSurah":52,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":577,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5548,"text":"Ah! Non! C'est plut\u00f4t qu'ils ne craignent pas l'au-del\u00e0.","numberInSurah":53,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":577,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5549,"text":"Ah! Non! Ceci est vraiment un Rappel.","numberInSurah":54,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":577,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5550,"text":"Quiconque veut, qu'il se le rappelle.","numberInSurah":55,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":577,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false},{"number":5551,"text":"Mais ils ne se rappelleront que si Allah veut. C'est Lui qui est Le plus digne d'\u00eatre craint; et c'est Lui qui d\u00e9tient le pardon.","numberInSurah":56,"juz":29,"manzil":7,"page":577,"ruku":511,"hizbQuarter":230,"sajda":false}],"edition":{"identifier":"fr.hamidullah","language":"fr","name":"Hamidullah","englishName":"Muhammad Hamidullah","format":"text","type":"translation","direction":"ltr"}}}